com.jayway.changeless.vectors
Class VectorSupport<T>

java.lang.Object
  com.jayway.changeless.vectors.VectorSupport<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of the elements in this vector.
All Implemented Interfaces:
Sequenceable<T>, Vector<T>, Iterable<T>
public abstract class VectorSupport<T>
extends Object
implements Vector<T>

A support class for easily implement Vector's. To implement your own Vector you need to implements the following methods: add, get, set, size.
